\c 10
\s Isono sikaNadabi loAbihu
\p
\v 1 Amadodana kaAroni, oNadabi loAbihu\x + Eks. 6.23; 28.1; Levi 16.1; Nani 3.4; 26.61; 1 Lan. 24.2.\x*, asethatha ngulowo lalowo umganu wakhe wokutshisela impepha\x + Nani 16.18.\x*, afaka umlilo kiyo, abeka phezu kwawo impepha, anikela umlilo ongejwayelekanga phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 30.9.\x*\nd*, eyayingawalayanga wona.
\v 2 Kwasekuphuma umlilo ovela phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 9.24. Nani 16.35. 2 Sam. 6.7.\x*\nd*, wawaqothula, asefela phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 3 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni: Yilokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakukhulumayo isithi: Kulabo abasondela kimi\x + 21.17,21. Isa. 52.11.\x* ngizangcweliswa, futhi phambi kwabantu bonke ngizadunyiswa\x + Hez. 28.22.\x*. UAroni wasethula\x + Hlab. 39.9.\x*.
\v 4 UMozisi wasebiza uMishayeli loElizafani, amadodana kaUziyeli uyise omncane kaAroni\x + Eks. 6.18,22. Nani 3.19,30.\x*, wathi kibo: Sondelani, libasuse abafowenu phambi kwendlu engcwele\x + Gen. 29.12.\x*, kuze kube ngaphandle kwenkamba.
\v 5 Basondela-ke, babathwala bembethe izigqoko zabo kwaze kwaba ngaphandle kwenkamba, njengokutsho kukaMozisi.
\v 6 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni lakuEleyazare lakuIthamari, amadodana akhe: Lingembuli amakhanda enu\x + 13.45; 21.10. Hez. 24.16,17.\x*, lingadabuli izembatho zenu, hlezi life, lolaka lwehlele phezu kwenhlangano yonke\x + Nani 1.53. 16.22,46; 18.5. Josh. 22.18,20.\x*. Kodwa akuthi abafowenu, indlu yonke kaIsrayeli, balilele ukutshisa iN\nd kosi\nd* ekuphembileyo.
\v 7 Lingaphumi ngomnyango wethente lenhlangano\x + 21.12.\x* hlezi life, ngoba amafutha okugcoba eN\nd kosi\nd* aphezu kwenu\x + 8.30.\x*. Benza-ke njengelizwi likaMozisi.
\p
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuAroni isithi:
\v 9 Unganathi iwayini lokunathwayo okulamandla\x + Hez.44.21; Luka 1.15.\x*, wena lamadodana akho kanye lawe, nxa lingena ethenteni lenhlangano, ukuze lingafi; kuyisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu;
\v 10 lokwehlukanisa phakathi kokungcwele lokungangcwele, laphakathi kokungahlambulukanga lokuhlambulukileyo\x + 11.47; 20.25; Hez. 22.26.\x*;
\v 11 lokufundisa abantwana bakoIsrayeli zonke izimiso iN\nd kosi\nd* ezikhulume kubo ngesandla sikaMozisi\x + 14.57. Dute. 24.8; Hez. 44.23; Jer. 18.18. Mal. 2.7.\x*.
\v 12 UMozisi wasesithi kuAroni lakuEleyazare lakuIthamari, amadodana akhe ayesele: Thathani umnikelo wokudla\x + 6.16; Nani 18.9,10.\x* oseleyo eminikelweni yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo, liwudle ungelamvubelo eceleni kwelathi\x + 1.16.\x*, ngoba uyingcwelengcwele\x + 10.17; Eks. 40.10.\x*;
\v 13 njalo liwudlele endaweni engcwele, ngoba uyimfanelo yakho lemfanelo yamadodana akho, esivela eminikelweni yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo; ngoba ngilaywe njalo\x + 2.3; 6.16; 8.35.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa isifuba sokuzunguzwa\x + Eks. 29.24,26,27; Levi 7.31,34; Nani 18.11.\x* lomlenze wokuphakanyiswa lizakudlela endaweni ehlambulukileyo, wena lamadodana akho, lamadodakazi akho kanye lawe; ngoba kuyisabelo sakho lesabelo samadodana akho; kunikwa kuvela emihlatshelweni yeminikelo yokuthula yabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 15 Umlenze wokuphakanyiswa lesifuba sokuzunguzwa bazakuletha leminikelo yamahwahwa eyenziwe ngomlilo, ukukuzunguza kube ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; kuzakuba ngokwakho lokwamadodana akho kanye lawe, kube yisimiso saphakade, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 16 UMozisi wadingisisa impongo yomnikelo wesono\x + 9.3,15.\x*, khangela-ke yayitshisiwe. Ngakho wathukuthelela uEleyazare loIthamari, amadodana kaAroni aseleyo, esithi:
\v 17 Kalidlanga ngani umnikelo wesono endaweni engcwele\x + 6.26,29.\x*, ngoba uyingcwelengcwele, futhi ilinikile wona lina ukuze lithwale ububi benhlangano, libenzele inhlawulo yokuthula phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*?
\v 18 Khangelani, igazi lawo kalingeniswanga\x + 6.30.\x* phakathi e\add ndawe\add*ni engcwele\x + 10.4.\x*. Ngabe isibili liyidlile e\add ndawe\add*ni engcwele njengokulaya kwami\x + 6.26.\x*.
\v 19 UAroni wasesithi kuMozisi: Khangela, lamuhla sebenikele umnikelo wabo wesono lomnikelo wabo wokutshiswa phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 9.8,12.\x*\nd*, kanti izinto ezinje zingehlele! Uba bengidlile umnikelo wesono lamuhla, bekuzakuba kuhle emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* yini?
\v 20 Esezwile lokho uMozisi kwaba kuhle emehlweni akhe.